<Layout>
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>Yohta Kitagawa is a Japanese critical media artist. He primarily creates realtime systems that critiqe dominant concepts through personal and entangled experience.
        Yohta is currently studying abroad at Brown University, while conducting research with Rhode Island School of Design faculty.
        His primary medium is sound, choreographical performance, robotics.</p>
